{"audiobook":{"id":701,"slug":"okamzita-pomoc-proti-uzkosti-hanson-mckay","name":"Okam\u017eit\u00e1 pomoc proti \u00fazkosti","name_sub":"Jak nal\u00e9zt klid pr\u00e1v\u011b te\u010f a jak se postavit obav\u00e1m a \u00fazkostem","length":199,"size":182,"format":"MP3 ke sta\u017een\u00ed","description":"<p><strong>\u010cty\u0159icet nejjednodu\u0161\u0161\u00edch a nejefektivn\u011bj\u0161\u00edch technik<\/strong> pro okam\u017eit\u00e9 zklidn\u011bn\u00ed \u00fazkosti. Objevte v\u011bdecky ov\u011b\u0159en\u00e9 postupy od p\u0159edn\u00edch odborn\u00edk\u016f na du\u0161evn\u00ed zdrav\u00ed, kter\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eete pou\u017e\u00edt kdykoli a kdekoli pot\u0159ebujete naj\u00edt klid.<\/p><p><strong>Rick Hanson<\/strong>, renomovan\u00fd psycholog a neurov\u011bdec (autor bestseller\u016f Buddh\u016fv mozek a Sta\u010d\u00ed jen m\u00e1lo), spole\u010dn\u011b s <strong>Matthewem McKayem<\/strong> a t\u00fdmem \u0161pi\u010dkov\u00fdch terapeut\u016f p\u0159in\u00e1\u0161ej\u00ed soubor praktick\u00fdch n\u00e1stroj\u016f vyzkou\u0161en\u00fdch v re\u00e1ln\u00e9 praxi s tis\u00edci klient\u016f.<\/p><ul><li><p><strong>Okam\u017eit\u00e9 techniky pro zklidn\u011bn\u00ed<\/strong> mysli v stresov\u00fdch situac\u00edch<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Kognitivn\u011b-behavior\u00e1ln\u00ed postupy<\/strong> pro zvl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed katastrofick\u00fdch my\u0161lenek<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Mindfulness cvi\u010den\u00ed<\/strong> pro n\u00e1vrat do p\u0159\u00edtomn\u00e9ho okam\u017eiku<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Relaxa\u010dn\u00ed techniky<\/strong> zalo\u017een\u00e9 na neurov\u011bdeck\u00fdch poznatc\u00edch<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Praktick\u00e9 n\u00e1stroje<\/strong> pro dlouhodob\u00e9 zvl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed \u00fazkost\u00ed<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>Audiokniha nep\u0159in\u00e1\u0161\u00ed jen teorii, ale <strong>40 konkr\u00e9tn\u00edch, rychl\u00fdch a efektivn\u00edch technik<\/strong>, kter\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eete okam\u017eit\u011b za\u010d\u00edt pou\u017e\u00edvat. Ka\u017ed\u00fd postup je v\u011bdecky ov\u011b\u0159en\u00fd a prax\u00ed prov\u011b\u0159en\u00fd - od mindfulness p\u0159es kognitivn\u011b-behavior\u00e1ln\u00ed terapii a\u017e po nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed poznatky neurov\u011bd.<\/p><h2>Poznatky, kter\u00e9 zm\u011bn\u00ed v\u00e1\u0161 pohled<\/h2><ul><li><p><strong>\u00dazkost je norm\u00e1ln\u00ed reakce<\/strong> - m\u00e1te pln\u00e9 pr\u00e1vo na sv\u00e9 vnit\u0159n\u00ed pro\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Katastrofick\u00e9 my\u0161lenky lze zastavit<\/strong> pomoc\u00ed konkr\u00e9tn\u00edch technik<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Klid m\u016f\u017eete naj\u00edt kdykoli<\/strong> - sta\u010d\u00ed zn\u00e1t spr\u00e1vn\u00e9 postupy<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Relaxace je dovednost<\/strong>, kterou se lze nau\u010dit<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Mal\u00e9 zm\u011bny vedou k velk\u00fdm v\u00fdsledk\u016fm<\/strong> v oblasti du\u0161evn\u00ed pohody<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>\u017dijeme v nejist\u00e9 dob\u011b pln\u00e9 stresu a obav. Pokud v\u00e1m hlavou b\u011b\u017e\u00ed rozli\u010dn\u00e9 my\u0161lenky, to\u010d\u00edte se v kruhu katastrofick\u00fdch sc\u00e9n\u00e1\u0159\u016f nebo se boj\u00edte o sebe \u010di sv\u00e9 bl\u00edzk\u00e9, <strong>tato audiokniha v\u00e1m pom\u016f\u017ee se \u201ehodit do klidu\"<\/strong>.<\/p><p>Autorsk\u00fd t\u00fdm slo\u017een\u00fd z <strong>p\u0159edn\u00edch americk\u00fdch odborn\u00edk\u016f<\/strong> v oblasti pom\u00e1haj\u00edc\u00edch profes\u00ed vytvo\u0159il praktick\u00fd pr\u016fvodce, kter\u00fd v\u00e1m pom\u016f\u017ee nejen c\u00edtit se l\u00e9pe, ale tak\u00e9 <strong>\u017e\u00edt v souladu s t\u00edm, co je pro v\u00e1s opravdu podstatn\u00e9<\/strong>.<\/p><p>C\u00edlem nen\u00ed potla\u010dit \u00fazkost, ale <strong>nau\u010dit se s n\u00ed konstruktivn\u011b pracovat<\/strong>, zlep\u0161it si n\u00e1ladu a porozum\u011bt sami sob\u011b. V\u0161echny techniky jsou <strong>zalo\u017een\u00e9 na d\u016fkazech<\/stron